lead_paragraph: Benoit Cheyrou and Tosaint Ricketts scored 2 minutes apart in extra time and Toronto FC advanced to the MLS Cup final, outlasting the Montreal Impact 5-2 in the rain Wednesday night for a 7-5 aggregate victory.

headline.print_headline: Toronto FC Outlasts Montreal to Reach MLS Cup Final
